Based on your *description*, you can use `lag()` and a cumulative sum.  To get the journeys:

    select id, date, journey, min(time), max(time)
    from (select t.*,
                 sum(case when prev_time &gt; dateadd(minute, -90, time) then 0 else 1 end) over
                     (partition by id, date order by time) as journey
          from (select lag(time) over (partition by id, date order by time) as prev_time
                from t
               ) t
         ) t
    group by id, date, journey;

If you just want to count them:

    select sum(case when prev_time &gt; dateadd(minute, -90, time) then 0 else 1 end) 
    from (select lag(time) over (partition by id, date order by time) as prev_time
          from t
         ) t;

